      <div class="col-sm-8">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-6 pb-4">
            <h4>Status & Presence</h4>
            <p class="fs-sm">See if other users are currently on a call. Light shows green for available or red if that user is on a call.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6 pb-4">
            <h4>Call Parking</h4>
            <p class="fs-sm">Move incoming calls to a parked area to hand-off calls between team members.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-6 pb-4">
            <h4>Wired Headsets</h4>
            <p class="fs-sm">Crisp, clear and dependable, wired headsets are an effective way to enable a hands free experience.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <h4>Intercom</h4>
            <p class="fs-sm">With the press of a button instantly start a conversation with another user over speakerphone.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-6 pb-4">
            <h4>Paging</h4>
            <p class="fs-sm">Communicate quickly or find someone in a large space with paging.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6 pb-4">
            <h4>Wifi</h4>
            <p class="fs-sm">Cut the cord and enjoy additional mobility with wifi-enabled phones.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <h4>Bluetooth</h4>
            <p class="fs-sm">Most of our phones support Bluetooth so you can connect wireless headsets, AirPods, and more.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <h4>Call History</h4>
            <p class="fs-sm">See recent calls or sort by incoming, outgoing, missed and internal calls right from the onscreen menu of your phone.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
